Package: HASr
Type: Package
Title: Hefei Aging Study (HAS) Data Processing and Analysis Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-07-28
Authors@R: c(
    person("HAS Research Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "has@ustc.edu.cn"),
    person("University of Science and Technology of China", role = "cph")
    )
Description: A comprehensive R package for processing and analyzing data from the 
    Hefei Aging Study (HAS) cohort. This package provides functions for data 
    cleaning, variable extraction, and statistical analysis of demographic, 
    neurological, musculoskeletal, cardiovascular, endocrine, immunological, 
    and cerebrovascular health indicators in urban aging populations. The HAS 
    cohort focuses on healthy aging progression in Luyang District, Hefei, 
    integrating clinical, cognitive, imaging, and biomarker data from adults 
    aged 50 and older.
